query:
SELECT i.id, i.productId, p.sku, i.status, i.quantity, i.tenantId, t.name as tenantName
FROM inventory i
LEFT JOIN products p ON i.productId = p.id
LEFT JOIN tenants t ON i.tenantId = t.id
WHERE i.status != 'available'
LIMIT 20;
